    "It was during this time that he wrote <em>Klassische Kunst</em> (1898) which was to become one of his most popular books.": [],
    "In 1901 W\u00f6lfflin was called to the prestigious University of Berlin to become <em>Ordinarius</em> professor of the University, succeeding the popular <a href=\"/grimmh\">Herman Grimm</a>.": [
        [
