    "He ran an art history institute in Berlin lead by the talented art historian/polymath <a href=\"/waetzoldtw\">Wilhelm Waetzoldt</a>.": [],
    "Students to his lectures in Berlin included <a href=\"/gombriche\">E.": [],
    "H. Gombrich</a> (who was impressed with W\u00f6lfflin's delivery style but not methodology).": [
